<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 16:07:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>活动人士称，加沙援助船队在船只旗帜被移除后停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/gaza-aid-flotilla-halted-after-vessels-flag-removed-activists-say/0000018f-2553-d1f3-afcf-2f73993e0000</link><description>该船队将于周五从土耳其港口起航，船上载有超过 5,000 吨援助物资。活动人士称几内亚比绍当局的检查和要求是不寻常的和政治性的</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 15:40:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/gaza-aid-flotilla-halted-after-vessels-flag-removed-activists-say/0000018f-2553-d1f3-afcf-2f73993e0000</guid></item><item><title>谢丽尔·桑德伯格的电影为以色列哈马斯性暴力受害者发声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/sheryl-sandbergs-film-gives-voice-to-israeli-victims-of-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018f-2481-d502-a5bf-e4e7d8800000</link><description>在纽约举行的《沉默前的尖叫》首映式上，这位前 Meta 高管表示，这部纪录片将有助于消除人们对哈马斯大规模实施性暴力的否认。该片导演阿纳特·斯大林斯基表示：“以色列不是一个经历过创伤的国家，而是一个处于创伤后阶段的国家。”它正在经历持续的创伤”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 15:27:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/sheryl-sandbergs-film-gives-voice-to-israeli-victims-of-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018f-2481-d502-a5bf-e4e7d8800000</guid></item><item><title>拉法不是加沙的斯大林格勒。这是内塔尼亚胡的又一次操纵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/rafah-is-not-gazas-stalingrad-its-another-manipulation-by-netanyahu/0000018f-2496-d0a5-abcf-37fe560b0000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登的计划可能会真正改变加沙和中东的游戏规则 — — 而且现在比去年更加可行。但当本杰明·内塔尼亚胡仍在以色列发号施令时就不会了</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 15:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/rafah-is-not-gazas-stalingrad-its-another-manipulation-by-netanyahu/0000018f-2496-d0a5-abcf-37fe560b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列球迷因穿着反本格维尔衬衫而被拒绝观看比赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soccer-fan-denied-access-to-game-for-wearing-anti-ben-gvir-shirt/0000018f-24de-dc45-a78f-3edf07650000</link><description>罗伊·巴尔坎 (Roi Barkan) 和一位朋友表示，他们被禁止观看特拉维夫的一场足球比赛，因为他们穿着写有“FCK BNGVR”的衬衫。警方还获取了他们的个人信息</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 14:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soccer-fan-denied-access-to-game-for-wearing-anti-ben-gvir-shirt/0000018f-24de-dc45-a78f-3edf07650000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦总统表示只有美国才能制止以色列对拉法的袭击，预计几天之内</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/palestinian-president-says-only-u-s-can-halt-israels-attack-on-rafah-expected-in-days/0000018f-242d-d1f3-afcf-2f6d678c0000</link><description>马哈茂德·阿巴斯在利雅得举行的世界经济论坛特别会议上发表讲话，呼吁美国“要求以色列不要继续发动袭击”，他认为这可能会导致“巴勒斯坦人民历史上最大的灾难”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 10:55:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/palestinian-president-says-only-u-s-can-halt-israels-attack-on-rafah-expected-in-days/0000018f-242d-d1f3-afcf-2f6d678c0000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家发现墓地可能与古代以色列人有关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-04-28/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-find-cemetery-possibly-linked-to-the-ancient-israelites/0000018f-2344-dacd-a7ef-37c510fb0000</link><description>考古学家称，位于耶斯列山谷的 Horvat Tevet 墓地是罕见的发现，是迦南城邦末期和 3000 多年前圣经以色列王国诞生时期的罕见发现</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-04-28/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-find-cemetery-possibly-linked-to-the-ancient-israelites/0000018f-2344-dacd-a7ef-37c510fb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列令人垂涎的拉法行动是战略目标还是讨价还价的筹码？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/is-israels-coveted-rafah-operation-a-strategic-target-or-a-bargaining-chip/0000018f-2160-dacd-a7ef-37e1dd300000</link><description>对于埃及来说，结束战争与哈马斯一样至关重要，而拉法行动的准备工作可能会加剧人道主义危机，使埃及与以色列的关系紧张，并导致大量加沙人越过边境，这使得埃及调解人 利害关系方</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 03:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/is-israels-coveted-rafah-operation-a-strategic-target-or-a-bargaining-chip/0000018f-2160-dacd-a7ef-37e1dd300000</guid></item><item><title>人们对哈马斯人质协议寄予厚望，但我们以前见过这种情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/hopes-are-high-for-a-hamas-hostage-deal-but-weve-seen-this-before/0000018f-2116-d0a5-abcf-37fe65380000</link><description>埃及对新一轮谈判的预测是乐观的，但以色列极右翼部长和哈马斯都可能构成不可逾越的障碍。虽然内塔尼亚胡担心国际刑事法院检察官，但如果未达成协议，甘茨和艾森科特退出政府的可能性越来越大</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 03:00:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/hopes-are-high-for-a-hamas-hostage-deal-but-weve-seen-this-before/0000018f-2116-d0a5-abcf-37fe65380000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯代表团周一访问开罗参加加沙停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article-live/idf-says-26-launches-to-meron-area-in-israels-north-fell-in-open-territories/0000018f-2258-dacd-a7ef-37d9f4ca0000</link><description>战时内阁部长甘茨表示，如果阻止人质交易，政府将无权存在 ■ 国防部长加兰特对参与袭击巴勒斯坦人的五名定居者签署行政逮捕令 ■ 财政部长斯莫特里奇要求内塔尼亚胡不要取消拉法行动 ■ 法国外长访问黎巴嫩 ■ 哈马斯官员称，哈马斯代表团将访问开罗进行加沙会谈</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 01:54:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article-live/idf-says-26-launches-to-meron-area-in-israels-north-fell-in-open-territories/0000018f-2258-dacd-a7ef-37d9f4ca0000</guid></item><item><title>从以色列监狱释放的巴勒斯坦人描述殴打、性虐待和酷刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinian-released-from-israeli-prison-describes-beatings-sexual-abuse-and-torture/0000018f-15e9-d2e1-a7df-15efb6590000</link><description>阿米尔·阿布·哈利勒 (Amer Abu Halil) 是约旦河西岸居民，曾活跃于哈马斯，未经审判就被监禁，他回忆起他在以色列凯齐奥特监狱 (Ketziot Prison) 的战时生活</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 21:05:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinian-released-from-israeli-prison-describes-beatings-sexual-abuse-and-torture/0000018f-15e9-d2e1-a7df-15efb6590000</guid></item><item><title>加沙谈判消息来源：哈马斯提供了可行的以色列人质人数，表明积极的转变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/source-in-gaza-talks-hamas-presenting-feasible-hostage-numbers-indicating-positive-shift/0000018f-2116-d1f3-afcf-2b778bbc0000</link><description>消息人士称，作为一种谈判策略，哈马斯一直在夸大其能够运送人质的数量，这有望表明其愿意推动达成协议。一名外交官员表示，以色列尚未同意停止战斗或从加沙撤军</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 20:09:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/source-in-gaza-talks-hamas-presenting-feasible-hostage-numbers-indicating-positive-shift/0000018f-2116-d1f3-afcf-2b778bbc0000</guid></item><item><title>这些抗议人道主义援助的以色列人现在把目光投向了解决加沙问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/these-israelis-protesting-humanitarian-aid-now-have-their-sights-set-on-settling-gaza/0000018f-207d-d1f3-afcf-2b7da58b0000</link><description>几个月来，极右宗教犹太复国主义活动人士一直在监视以色列加沙边境地区，准备突破围栏，进入加沙，并最终重建犹太人定居点。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 18:44:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/these-israelis-protesting-humanitarian-aid-now-have-their-sights-set-on-settling-gaza/0000018f-207d-d1f3-afcf-2b7da58b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议执政联盟，要求达成人质协议；七人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-government-demand-hostage-deal/0000018f-2059-d0a5-abcf-37f966dc0000</link><description>一名被扣押在加沙的人质的母亲说，“哈马斯和[以色列]政府的心肠越来越硬，政府正在对我发起一场运动”，同时以色列所有主要城市都在发生示威活动</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 18:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-government-demand-hostage-deal/0000018f-2059-d0a5-abcf-37f966dc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 204 天：哈马斯播放两名以色列人质的视频，其中一名拥有美国公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-204-hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-hostages-one-with-u-s-citizenship/0000018f-2049-d0a5-abcf-37f99a680000</link><description>哈马斯正在研究以色列对停火谈判立场的反应 ■ 塞浦路斯恢复向加沙运送援助物资 ■ 以色列国防军：两名巴勒斯坦人在西岸以色列国防军前哨基地开火后丧生 ■ 亲巴勒斯坦抗议领袖被禁止进入哥伦比亚大学校园 ■ 以下是您需要了解的信息战争开始204天</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 16:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-204-hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-hostages-one-with-u-s-citizenship/0000018f-2049-d0a5-abcf-37f99a680000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯播放了两名以色列人质在加沙被囚禁的视频，其中一名是美国公民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-two-israeli-hostages-one-with-u-s-citizenship-in-gaza-captivity/0000018f-205b-d0a5-abcf-37fb81010000</link><description>该视频描绘了 10 月 7 日在加沙边境社区的家中被绑架的人质奥姆里·米兰 (Omri Miran) 和基思·西格尔 (Keith Seigel)。可以看到他们向家人和政府发表讲话</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 16:46:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-two-israeli-hostages-one-with-u-s-citizenship-in-gaza-captivity/0000018f-205b-d0a5-abcf-37fb81010000</guid></item><item><title>“每次我们接近达成协议时，双方都会进行破坏”：卡塔尔高级官员告诉国土报，以色列和哈马斯都应该受到指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/every-time-were-close-to-a-deal-both-sides-sabotage-it-top-qatari-official-to-haaretz/0000018f-1f94-d1f3-afcf-3ff5ab730000</link><description>“我们想拯救人的生命，但卡塔尔成为那些试图保护其政治未来的人的出气筒。”卡塔尔总理顾问马吉德·安萨里博士在首次接受以色列媒体采访时告诉国土报，以色列和哈马斯没有表现出足够的承诺来达成停火/释放人质协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 16:09:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/every-time-were-close-to-a-deal-both-sides-sabotage-it-top-qatari-official-to-haaretz/0000018f-1f94-d1f3-afcf-3ff5ab730000</guid></item><item><title>英国广播公司报道称，英国军队可能负责向近海码头运送加沙援助物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/british-troops-may-be-tasked-with-delivering-gaza-aid-to-offshore-pier-bbc-report-says/0000018f-2005-dc45-a78f-3e4dbf4b0000</link><description>该报告发布之前，一名美国高级军事官员表示，不会有美国“地面部队”，另一个国家将提供人员将运货卡车开往加沙海岸</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 15:13:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/british-troops-may-be-tasked-with-delivering-gaza-aid-to-offshore-pier-bbc-report-says/0000018f-2005-dc45-a78f-3e4dbf4b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方记录：本-格维尔的司机曾因超速被定罪，驾照被暂时吊销</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/police-records-ben-gvirs-driver-once-convicted-of-speeding-license-temporarily-revoked/0000018f-1f31-d502-a5bf-fff7f6350000</link><description>这名司机也是本-格维尔安保人员的成员，他在西岸路线上被发现以几乎两倍于法定速度限制的速度行驶。他的驾照被吊销50天并被罚款</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 13:39:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/police-records-ben-gvirs-driver-once-convicted-of-speeding-license-temporarily-revoked/0000018f-1f31-d502-a5bf-fff7f6350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方逮捕了七名试图向加沙提供援助的犹太人，其中包括五名美国犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-arrest-seven-including-five-u-s-jews-trying-to-bring-aid-into-gaza/0000018f-1e6d-dc45-a78f-1e6de0940000</link><description>以色列出生的美国作家阿耶莱特·瓦尔德曼 (Ayelet Waldman) 是被捕者之一，目前仍被拘留。她是拉比人权组织的美国代表团的成员，该代表团试图向加沙地带的巴勒斯坦人提供救济，并呼吁结束战争</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 08:10:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-arrest-seven-including-five-u-s-jews-trying-to-bring-aid-into-gaza/0000018f-1e6d-dc45-a78f-1e6de0940000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯表示正在审查以色列的停火协议提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-it-received-israels-response-to-its-position-over-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-1de5-dacd-a7ef-3fe5d9bc0000</link><description>哈马斯发表声明的前一天，埃及代表团抵达以色列，试图重启谈判。据《阿拉伯报》报道，埃及代表团成员包括埃及情报局长。一名美国官员周四表示，目前的提议几乎满足了哈马斯的所有要求</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 05:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-it-received-israels-response-to-its-position-over-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-1de5-dacd-a7ef-3fe5d9bc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>